Business::Tax::VAT::Validation version 0.02
===========================================

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   $ tar -zxvf Business-Tax-VAT-Validation-x.xx.tar.gz
   $ cd  Business-Tax-VAT-Validation-x.xx

   $ perl Makefile.PL
   $ make
   $ make test
   # make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries available at CPAN:

    HTTP::Request::Common
    LWP::UserAgent

